\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{Y}=\mathbb{Y}^{\left(1\right)}\times\mathbb{Y}^{\left(2\right)}$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{Y}^{\left(i\right)}$
\end_inset

 is the measure induced by the 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

th coordinate of 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{Y}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
