\begin_inset Formula $\tau^{\left(i\right)}=\inf\{t\in[0,1)\mid\mathbf{X}_{t}^{\nu,\left(i\right)}=\bar{\mathbf{X}}_{1-t}^{\nu,\left(\setminus i\right)}\}$
\end_inset

